Package: parsetools
Title: Tools for building parsers with R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Taras", "Zakharko",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "taras.zakharko@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7601-8424"))
Description: This package provides a modular infrastructure for building
    ergonomic text parsers. It implements a lightweight consumable text 
    buffer with value semantics and facility to generate flexible parsers
    from a formal description. Parser performance is not a focus of this
    package, as it is primarily meant for prototyping parsers and creating
    compact DSLs.
